<inglise> - Individual Detriment: clinically observable deleterious effects that are expressed in individuals or their descendants, the appearance of which is either immediate or delayed and, in the latter case, implies a probability rather than a certainty of appearance. </inglise>
<eesti> isikukahjustus - kliiniliselt tuvastav kahjulik m&otilde;ju, mis avaldub &uuml;ksikisikutes v&otilde;i nende j&auml;reltulijates ja mis ilmneb kohe v&otilde;i viivitusega, kusjuures viimasel juhul on tegu pigem t&otilde;en&auml;olise kui kindla ilmnemisega; </eesti>
<inglise> - Inspection: inspection is an investigation by any competent authority to verify compliance with national provisions on radiological protection for medical radiological procedures, equipment in use or radiological installations. </inglise>
<eesti> inspekteerimine - m&otilde;ne p&auml;deva asutuse tehtav uurimine, mille eesm&auml;rk on teha kindlaks, kas meditsiiniradioloogia protseduuride, kasutatavate seadmete v&otilde;i radioloogiaasutuste osas t&auml;idetakse siseriiklikke kiirguskaitsenorme; </eesti>
<inglise> - Medical Physics Expert: an expert in radiation physics or radiation technology applied to exposure, within the scope of this Directive, whose training and competence to act is recognized by the competent authorities; and who, as appropriate, acts or gives advice on patient dosimetry, on the development and use of complex techniques and equipment, on optimization, on quality assurance, including quality control, and on other matters relating to radiation protection, concerning exposure within the scope of this Directive. </inglise>
<eesti> meditsiinif&uuml;&uuml;sika spetsialist - k&auml;esoleva direktiiviga h&otilde;lmatud kiiritamisel rakendatava kiirgusf&uuml;&uuml;sika v&otilde;i -tehnoloogia spetsialist, kelle v&auml;lja&otilde;pet ja p&auml;devust on tunnustanud p&auml;devad asutused ja kes vajaduse korral m&auml;&auml;rab patsiendi dosimeetria, arendab ja kasutab keerulisi v&otilde;tteid ja seadmeid, optimeerib kiirguse, tagab kvaliteedi, sealhulgas ohjab seda, ja tegeleb muude kiirguskaitsek&uuml;simustega, mis on seotud k&auml;esoleva direktiiviga h&otilde;lmatud kiiritusega, v&otilde;i annab nimetatud asjades n&otilde;u; </eesti>
<inglise> - Medical Radiological Procedure: any procedure concerning medical exposure. </inglise>
