<inglise> - existing types of practices involving medical exposure may be reviewed whenever new, important evidence about their efficacy or consequences is acquired. </inglise>
<eesti> - v&otilde;ib l&auml;bi vaadata olemasolevad toimingud, millega kaasneb meditsiinikiiritus, kui saadakse uusi ja t&auml;htsaid t&otilde;endeid nende t&otilde;hususe v&otilde;i tagaj&auml;rgede kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) all individual medical exposures shall be justified in advance taking into account the specific objectives of the exposure and the characteristics of the individual involved. </inglise>
<eesti> b) p&otilde;hjendatakse &uuml;ksikisiku meditsiinikiiritust iga kord eelnevalt, v&otilde;ttes arvesse kiiritamise erieesm&auml;rke ja asjaomase &uuml;ksikisiku erijooni. </eesti>
<inglise> If a type of practice involving a medical exposure is not justified in general, a specific individual exposure of this type could be justified in special circumstances, to be evaluated on a case-by-case basis. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui teatav toiming, millega kaasneb meditsiinikiiritus, ei ole &uuml;ldiselt p&otilde;hjendatud, v&otilde;ib &uuml;ksikisiku sedalaadi kiiritamist p&otilde;hjendada eriasjaoludel, mida hinnatakse igal &uuml;ksikjuhul eraldi. </eesti>
<inglise> The prescriber and the practitioner as specified by Member States, shall seek, where practicable, to obtain previous diagnostic information or medical records relevant to the planned exposure and consider these data to avoid unnecessary exposure. </inglise>
<eesti> Radioloogiaprotseduurile suunav arst ja radioloogiaprotseduuri tegev arst p&uuml;&uuml;avad, nagu liikmesriigid on ette n&auml;inud, v&otilde;imaluse korral hankida kavandatava kiiritamise seisukohast olulisi varasemaid diagnostilisi v&otilde;i tervisekaardiandmeid ja need l&auml;bi vaadata, et v&auml;ltida asjatut kiiritamist; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) medical exposure for biomedical and medical research shall be examined by an ethics committee, set up in accordance with national procedures and/or by the competent authorities. </inglise>
